{"tid":2352743,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"有港人趕於深圳實施入境檢疫新安排前返回內地","createTime":"2021-01-04T08:28:38.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-04T08:38:55.000Z","uid":41404,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"7e0412c2f5b9385c3616ea93e88f6db883f57b43","tid":2352743,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T08:28:38.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1568551-20210104.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1568551-20210104.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=qAbY1fQWWFezl0O3VAvZyc5Q2JFdPMmcxM5Tq6mQO7A%3D&h=a4c23175\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1568551-20210104.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=69159532\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1568551-20210104.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"c618270eae755831d2f150b699df984eeb8fd3bd","tid":2352743,"uid":41404,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T08:28:52.000Z","msg":"賴太表示，原本打算等待六年級的女兒考試後，才回鄉過年，但無奈政策明天收緊，因此需要比計劃提早一星期返回內地。她說，由於升中遞表今日才開始，今早匆忙回校，今午就立刻過關回內地。<br />\n<br />\n有家人在內地的鄧同學表示，今日專程提早回鄉，對新安排感到倉促。她表示措施收緊後，再需要額外7天社區隔離，認為時間很漫長，而且學校現時為網上授課，因此選擇提早回鄉。<br />\n<br />\n另一名趕返內地的楊先生表示，得知消息後決定提早回內地過年，他認為措施收緊後，要預訂酒店很麻煩，而且不懂預約程序，批評有關安排交代得不清晰。"},{"pid":"0025705805f97a968b6b12e41ff88ee484aab7ab","tid":2352743,"uid":304769,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T08:29:35.000Z","msg":"港你老母<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">蝗蟲</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"85f2d6b1c94d50f26458f2ca6c837e97730e6eff","tid":2352743,"uid":286103,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T08:30:33.000Z","msg":"唔好再番尼喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"009dd826b6e8d9d22a681bab135be7e1c67abc2c","tid":2352743,"uid":522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedB